<div class="callout-box">
    <h3>Pension Assistance List (PAL) Actuary Network</h3>
    <p>The Pension Assistance List, or "PAL," is a nationwide referral service created by the <%= link_to 'American Academy of Actuaries', 'http://www.actuary.org/' %> to help individuals needing assistance with benefit calculations and comparisons. PAL actuaries and consultants generally charge for their services but will offer up to four hours of free help.</p>
